name: Mac App Icons V 1.4
description:
Do you like nice and simple icons like me? So enjoy them.


How to change the application icon in Mac OS? It's very easy and looks great.


Read the article on AppleInsider: https://appleinsider.com/articles/21/01/06/how-to-change-app-icons-on-macos


Or watch this video on YouTube: https://youtu.be/Y95U--xd5NM


Do you like the icons? Let me know in the comments what icon you would like me to add.
